storyInfo: Emerging from the illusion of their collective dream, the group comes face to face with the sudden appearance of Nian, and bears witness to her conflict with Dusk.

attributes.content: (So... this is Lungmen.)
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: (I must hurry—)
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Kind sir, would you spare me a moment?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Hmm?
There is something I would like to ask.
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Is Master Tung's finball stall nearby?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: You... You are not from Lungmen, are you?
Came to sample his reputed finballs, have you?
Uh, yes, but of course! They're famous far and wide, hahaha—
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Well, what time do you think it is? They closed for the day long ago.
If you truly want a bite, you'll want to line up at eight in the morning.
It has closed? Do you perchance know where Master Tung lives, then?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Hm...
Kind sir?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: You're here to sample his finballs. Why would his name or address matter to you at all?
Err... Hahaha, quite right. Haha... I'll wait till the morrow then—
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Young man...
Mmh—
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: —K-Kind sir? What is the meaning of this? Please, lower your cane—
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: What do you want with Tung?
I suggest you behave yourself here, young man. Now, explain.
You covered practically the entire town within just one night, from the old folks to the Greytails' boss. Now, you even ask for a finball hawker.
No one would come to this place to seek him out at this hour. Moreover... I know what it is that you are holding.
—You... Are you...?! Mmph!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Don't move, young man. Answer me first. Who else do you seek?
Only those I've already asked about! I am looking for Uncle Tung only because I have no choice—!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Is your name Lien?
No! No, it is not! Please, listen to me—
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Stop.
I am not one to mistake a man trained in the martial arts for a hooligan... And you hold the Lien clan's Yin-ch'ing fan. How are you related to Lien Tzu-hsu?
—She's my master!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: What became of her?
My master...
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: What became of her?!
She passed!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: ...How?
She... She was damned well murdered... because of me, an imbecile of a disciple!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: ...A shame.
Master Lin—!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Hmph... You know my name. How?
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: I-I heard of you from my master... Please, I cannot be caught by those men yet!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: You came here to Lungmen merely to drag out what time you have left.
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: The flame can't be snuffed!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: I suggest you go to the L.G.D.
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: This is nothing the police can manage!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Very well... Out of respect for Tung's friendship with your old master, I give you this chance.
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: You have three moves. Break my cane, and you may come with me.
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: —N-No, I can't!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Do it.
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: My master told me. The debt that Uncle Tung owes Lin of Lungmen... is also hers. No matter the circumstances, I must not disrespect—
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Do it!
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: —I'm afraid I can't!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: You coward! Unfold your fan!
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: My name is not Lien! I am undeserving!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Yet you hold her fan!!
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: Lien is not my name!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Then your master died for nothing!
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: I—
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Hm, well executed...
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: Master Lin... please forgive me.
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Stand up. I forced your hand. Nothing to kneel for.
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: Stay here in Lungmen for five years. After five years, I will send you back to Kou-wu City. What happens next, you'll have to figure out yourself.
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: Come.
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: Brother Nothing, are you really leaving?
attributes.name: Greytail

attributes.content: Stay in Lungmen. It's a nice place, no?
attributes.name: Greytail

attributes.content: I have yet to do what I must.
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Looks like we aren't keeping you here... Can we share one last drink, then?
attributes.name: Greytail

attributes.content: Save it. If I make it back alive, we will share this drink.
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: If that time comes, I suppose I won't be using this pseudonym anymore.
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: —Great!
attributes.name: Greytail

attributes.content: We await your return!
attributes.name: Greytail

attributes.content: So you really came back. That I did not expect...
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: But I must return. I am indebted to you. I cannot well just pack up and leave.
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Hoh. Look how much of a smooth-talker you've become. I wish you'd seen how nervous you were when we first met.
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: Ha. Haha, Master Lin. At least save me some face.
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: What's your plan after this?
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: It's all over, but I've made enemies everywhere. It's not realistic for me to stay in my hometown.
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: I've got a storefront downtown you can have. Not cheap, though.
attributes.name: Lin

attributes.content: Of course, I can't take what's yours without proper payment.
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: So this is your training hall, Brother?
attributes.name: Greytail

attributes.content: Indeed it is. I named it 'Friendship,' for friendship is wealth as the saying goes. What do you think?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Sounds kinda like a fitness center for the elderly...
attributes.name: Greytail

attributes.content: As long as it earns me good coin, why does it matter in this day and age that it's a fitness center for the elderly?!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Will anyone actually come...? Ugh, you charge the memberships by the year too?
attributes.name: Greytail

attributes.content: Ahaha... It's not necessarily a bad thing to have no customers. I heard this is fashionable in recent...
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Excuse me, is this a fitness center?
attributes.name: Lungmen Passerby

attributes.content: My oh my. Please come this way, esteemed guest. We are a traditional Yan martial arts training center. I guarantee you'll find yourself most hale and hearty in no time!
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Oh, I see. Give me a minute. Let me find my card.
attributes.name: Lungmen Passerby

attributes.content: You...
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Brother Nothing!
attributes.name: Greytail

attributes.content: Don't you think you're safe just because you're in Lungmen. You aren't getting away—
attributes.name: Lungmen Passerby

attributes.content: Bastard, die!
attributes.name: Greytail

attributes.content: Brother Nothing, are you alright?!
attributes.name: Greytail

attributes.content: Open your eyes... Do I look alright...?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Hang in there! I'll call an ambulance right away—
attributes.name: Greytail

attributes.content: Save it... *cough* *cough*... It's too late; I can tell. It's opening day, and blood has already been spilled. Just my luck...
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: I... *cough*, stop crying. You are a big guy. It's nothing uncommon to see a fellow man die.
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: I... I'm not... I...
attributes.name: Greytail

attributes.content: It's okay... This... is how it's meant to be...
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Brother Nothing!!
attributes.name: Greytail

attributes.content: Oh, so you aren't doing anything the rest of your life but avenging your master. You even had to kill yourself in your dream. Really, man?
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: I... Did I just...?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Did you what? If I didn't come fetch you, you'd have started all over again from the moment you left Kou-wu.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Now get up and get to work!
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: ...Why am I...
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Kroos! You're up!
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: ...Beagle?
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Why are you still... wearing your Rhodes Island outfit...?
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Hehe, we may be on vacation, but I really like it.
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: See? This part here is nice, right?
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: ...Is this your new place?
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Mm-hm!
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: Why don't you stay here for a few more days? I'll take real good care of you!
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: ...Yeah!
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Do we really need to go from here...?
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Shh!
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: Look over there...
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: ...Tsk, what a pain in the ass. That caravan barely had anything to take. Drew this big of a crowd here too! If I knew it'd be this much trouble, I wouldn't have taken the job!
attributes.name: Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: No use complaining now though. Hey, get the goods moved over here. That's a pretty good spot! Be sure to mark it down!
attributes.name: Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: —Bandits?
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Yeah, a Messenger said it's not very safe out on the mountains... So this is where they've all been hiding.
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: Kroos, we need to hurry back to tell security—
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: —Why? We can take care of them.
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Kroos, let's not get ahead of—
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: Hey, there's another caravan! Might be a merchant!
attributes.name: Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: We'll lose our chance if we don't hurry.
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: I never expected you of all people to say that...
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: Oh, looks like they're on the move! I'll protect—
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: —Huff!
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: You—?!
attributes.name: Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: Ugh?! What's wrong? Why did he pass out?!
attributes.name: Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: I'm here.
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Whoa... you took care of them all so quick... Even avoided their vitals so that they're only incapacitated.
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: When did you become such a badass?
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: Let's go get the guards.
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Sure!
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: *Yawn*... Morning.
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Hey, Kroos, did you sleep well?
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: I had to go to bed early all of a sudden. How was I supposed to fall asleep fine?
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Haha, but you know how early the Messengers leave. If you want to hitch a ride, you gotta head there early.
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: Oh, don't be like that. We just won't get to see each other for a while. You can come visit me any time.
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: Oh, and be sure to tell Fang I said hello. I wonder how she's doing these days...
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: Yeah.
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Hehe.
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: Okay, here's your luggage. I got it all packed up for you.
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: Yeah.
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Alright, enough with the sad face. Smile! You'll get to see Fang real soon!
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: Be sure to bring me some Columbian souvenirs!
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: ...Yeah!
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: See you, Kroos!
attributes.name: Beagle

attributes.content: We'll meet again, Beagle—
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: See you. We'll meet again.
You know that's not how things will end.
What you will face on the path ahead will be far worse.
I... knew you'd be here. Sorry, but I won't let you pass. No matter what.
What...? Did I just...
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: ...Finally awake, huh?
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Guard

attributes.content: We've been stuck here for a long time... Looks like you had a pretty sweet dream, though.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Guard

attributes.content: ...Sorry.
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: It's nothing to apologize for... but we're running out of rations, Kroos.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Guard

attributes.content: We gotta give it a shot, head to the other side of the valley and see what's going on there.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Guard

attributes.content: It's been way too long since we heard anything from the Bolívarian army. Did they change their route or something?
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Guard

attributes.content: Beagle...
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Anyway, we gotta leave. The mission was over a long time ago... We need to report back to Rhodes Island as well...
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Guard

attributes.content: No, this isn't right.
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: This isn't... This makes no sense...! The emergency comms aren't working!
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: B-But their camp shouldn't be that far away, going by the operation's map!
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Guard

attributes.content: Hey—! Where are you guys?!
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: T-This...
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: ...Beagle...? Are you sure it's her?
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: N-No way! How come?!
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: ...We'll have a detailed report later on.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Guard

attributes.content: And well... Kroos, we probably shouldn't get too involved in this mess... If Bolívar's really this complicated... there's nothing we can do for her.
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Guard

attributes.content: We need to head back to the Rhodes Island landship...
attributes.name: Rhodes Island Guard

attributes.content: You want me to stand by and watch her—
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: —No, I... I... I should've stopped her! I should've stopped her, whatever it took...!
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Hey, Kroos.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: ...Sorry, Nian, but I'm not in the mood to...
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Okay. Huh. Turns out Dusk couldn't have given you guys a better life, even in your dreams.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: All she did was draw the rest of your lives out in the painting and let them play out again from the beginning. It's all fake anyway. Couldn't you have picked a better ending?
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: What are you talking about—
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Don't worry, don't worry. Nian's here to save the day.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: I'm her big sister, after all.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Kroos! Mr. Nothing!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: It's so dark here... What's going on...?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I thought I saw the Umbrella-Boiler... put out the flames that he just lit up...?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: ...What's going on...?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hm, I wonder how things are going with Saga...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: ...There's ground beneath my feet, at least, but I gotta be careful...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Lava.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Waaahhh?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: N-Nian?! What are you doing here?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Oh, don't worry. I'm the real, 100% legit Nian you know and love, here to save you guys' asses.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: It's just, uh, how should I put this. She sure threw you for a loop...?
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: I can't see anything—
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: —Hold up, I can kinda make something out... Is there someone over there?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: That's a trap.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: She noticed what that thing I gave you is for, so she put all of you in some far-fetched, otherworldly dream right away. Too bad... got here a bit too late.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: How do you even do this?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: No idea. It's not that hard to carve a person's consciousness out of their minds. After all, the point wasn't to give you guys a second life. Fundamentally, it's more like... a kaleidoscope for you to reflect on and question yourself.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Whether it's a large mirror, a huge lake, or a vast sky full of stars, once you enter the painting, there is no way out. This is that almighty.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: I wonder why you alone are an exception, though. Oh, maybe it's cause we had all that hotpot together...?
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Don't drag me into a mess like this for a reason like that. Anyway, thanks.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Nian?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: ...Hm? Oh, it's nothing.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Wanna hear another story? Unlike Dusk, I'm not some uptight shut-in who hates the outdoors. This one isn't going to be nearly as boring.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Given the circumstances, I think we should worry about how to get out—
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Eh, you don't want to learn about how these people from the olden days fought off those Feranmuts when they were years behind with their industries, populations, and Originium Arts?
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: The last time you changed the conversation like that, we ended up with the Dark Devastator stuff.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Well, looks like you're interested.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: I... Whatever, go ahead...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: A long time ago, there existed many gods in the lands of Yan.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: The Yan emperor at the time saw his territory prosper, but his people suffered disasters and misfortunes one after another. He lamented this vicious cycle, and spent a long time to come up with a solution.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: He was the True Lung. Likely one of the most controversial men in Yan history, he was at the time still young in years, and his passion was unrivaled. As the emperor of Yan, he turned to his trusted retinue and told them this—
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: All the lands under heaven belong to the throne, and all men are my servants. Why then do the divinities above listen not to the will of the people of Great Yan and deprive our lands of their protection?
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: ...As you probably know, when the 'gods' are brought up in certain countries' folklore or history, they aren't necessarily merely philosophical concepts. That said, they aren't exactly all that mighty and revered either.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Case in point, the Lung found one such god deep in the mountains. A prideful and disdainful god.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Yan's long history was a brief stretch of time to him... Naturally, he didn't give any thought to the Lung's opinions, and he had no reason to care about the lives of mere mortals.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Now, this is where the problem lies. The Lung was too concerned with his subjects and his country.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: He issued and personally led his entire military, joined by many a formidable fighter, to take to the mountains on this wild hunt—
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: And... beyond anyone's expectations, being that the Lung first uncovered there decided to betray his kin and his fellow deities. It divided up its own strength, and participated in this once-in-a-lifetime wild hunt.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: After this great wild hunt, Yan slayed several of these 'gods' who dared to stand up against the Lung, and all those unwilling to submit to his rule were exiled.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Much blood was shed, and many lives were lost. Yan paid a dear price, and that's how this controversy surrounding the True Lung came to be.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: But he personally didn't care about this, and his campaign continued for as long as the Lung lived.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: When he was finally old and frail, he found the last such being remaining in Yan's lands. The most ancient and the most sacred. The eternal being that chose to betray its kin for the Lung's cause.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: The traitor had already received the justice it deserved. When its kin left the lands of Yan, they also took care to put out its flames of arrogance. Thus, its true nature was laid bare to the emperor—
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Anyway, its contributions had more than earned it the Lung's mercy. Nonetheless, the Lung forced it to serve Yan. To serve heaven, the lands, and its people to keep the world at peace.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Ever since, the fortunes of Yan have always belonged to the True Lung and his subjects.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: And at the same time, the so-called 'gods'—Though they had existed long before all the nations in the world came to be, they chose to hide themselves. They spread their own seeds across the land, placed the broken shards of their power and souls, and let them take root in this world in their place.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: They still exist in all shapes and forms across Terra, though their numbers are nowhere as great as before.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: But they all learned their lesson. Now, they're living across the world with everyone like one big family. Yep, it's a pretty good ending, don't you think?
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: You...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: ...Many nations have risen in Terra, and each one went through major changes throughout history. Yet, beyond Yan, there isn't a dynasty, a human who can tell this tale of the ennobling of the gods.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Yan is a real scary place.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Eh, anyway, let's blow this joint. I don't wanna stay here any longer.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: This painting is Dusk's trump card. We've got her indecisiveness to thank though. We wouldn't have a way out otherwise.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: ...H-How are you going to do that...?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: What... What happened to us...?
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Mnn, my brain hurts... Hmm? My benefactor, Kroos?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Nothing...? Where's Lava? Where's Saga?
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: No idea, they... M-My benefactor, are we back in Mount Hui-ch'i?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: ...Leave.
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: Who are you...?
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: I'll say this only once.
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: Don't tell me... You are Dusk?
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: This was Nian's idea, wasn't it?
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: I don't know who you people are, and I don't want to know what you've got to do with her. I don't care.
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: Now leave.
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: Don't tell me... You are the villain behind it all...?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: What if I am?
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: For someone who dared to disrupt my tranquility over and over, this is no punishment at all.
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: You don't mean, it's all because of the firecrackers...?
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: You've got it all wrong. We weren't trying to—
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: Wrong?
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: Nian may be able to fool you, but she can't fool me.
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: No matter what she says, I don't want to see her. Tell her that.
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: That's...
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: But what about Lava and Saga?
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: They—
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: What... Where?!
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.text: And smelt an edge to slice the sky!

attributes.content: W-What?! Where is this sound coming from?
attributes.name: Mr. Nothing

attributes.content: Get down!
attributes.name: Kroos

attributes.content: *cough* *cough*—
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: —What in the world did you come up with again?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Oh, it's just a big-ass firecracker. Eight feet long and three feet wide, uses the latest and greatest technology, never before seen in Terra, for its ignition!
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: You know how close I was? You could've at least warned me before you set that thing off!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: We didn't have the time. She would've gotten away again.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Isn't that right, my dear little sister?
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: —You.
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: How dare you burn my art!
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: Your art?
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Oh, I see. The moment we flung that door open, we'd already stepped into the world of your paintings, huh?
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Or are we in the middle of a hike? Maybe this whole mountain is just a fantasy that you've dreamt up?
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Oh, no wonder I could never find you, you unsociable loner—
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: W-What?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: That's right. I mean, you can't possibly hide all that junk in a cottage that small, can you? Are you telling me none of you figured that out?
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Hm, I guess most people's cognition and senses get affected, though. Can't blame you for not noticing, then.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: It's just like how you wouldn't feel anything's off no matter what kind of weird dream you have in your sleep.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Aha, you mad because I blew your little secret?
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: I'll beat you up and send you back to that mausoleum, 'Big Sis.'
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: Eh, that place was destroyed long ago.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Oh, perfect, then. It's time to build a new one, and we'll give its design a little more thought this time.
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: Hehe, you haven't changed at all. Always such a foulmouth when you're pissed... Did you just call me 'Big Sis' though?
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: ...You heard that right. After all, when you have to kill someone, it costs nothing to be cordial.
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: Don't worry, my 'little sister.' How many times have you defeated me?
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Don't be so confident, my all bark and no bite big sister.
attributes.name: Dusk

attributes.content: Well, I wonder about that, my cocky little sister.
attributes.name: Nian

attributes.content: Kroos, Mr. Nothing, hide!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.text: Heavenly forge, take the bounty of the earth and smelt an edge to slice the sky.
Starshrouded snow, hidden moon, let the crude mounts' waters sweep the streams.
